兩代人的節育政策與身體自主 （預告）"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"item_image":[{"_key":"77eae55bff75","_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-d785abba22ca9c25682e94af40cd2f1b6a54abb4-2160x1440-jpg","_type":"reference"},"published_time":"2022-08-01T13:09:52.315Z"}],"start_date":"2022-07-30","tags":[],"title":"「Not My Choice」"},{"_key":"011dcbf0cb76","_type":"timeline_item","description":[{"_key":"b1e55a34a059","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"dbe61dfe9634","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"人們如何作出「移民」這樣一個徹底重寫人生的選擇？是隨波逐流時忽然遇到分水嶺，還是駱駝身上那最後一根稻草壓下後才按下「重啟」鍵？在中國大陸，跨世代﹑跨階層的「潤學」紛紛擾擾；而在香港，持續的移民潮正在將香港記憶帶到遠方。可以肯定的是，「出走」的選項看似打開了一個更廣闊的世界，但連環的未知和不確定性，也在前方。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"c62b286e5575","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"9a987948ad29","_type":"span","marks":["717ea2793796"],"text":"想「潤」的60後：從文革到計劃生育，壓倒他們的最後一根稻草是上海封城"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[{"_key":"717ea2793796","_type":"link","href":"https://theinitium.com/article/20220727-mainland-run-60s/"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"bf624c12ea5c","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"2c7275c77b331","_type":"span","marks":["4aacacdceb81"],"text":"豪賭人生下半場：移民路上的中國中產"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[{"_key":"4aacacdceb81","_type":"link","href":"https://theinitium.com/article/20220617-mainland-middle-class-immigration/"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"f2495216de2a","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"4c42c895166a0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"澳洲「移民之島」塔斯曼尼亞上的華人（預告）"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"b6437a14a8fa","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"ab2379971c81","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"【端小聚】異鄉港人的鄉味與鄉愁（預告）"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"item_image":[{"_key":"acfb37c0425c","_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-19bb62d58e47979c939ec07404ae493caaf103bc-2160x1440-jpg","_type":"reference"},"published_time":"2022-08-01T13:09:29.348Z"}],"start_date":"2022-07-30","tags":[],"title":"「出走的選項」"},{"_key":"24d3f4e87ea1","_type":"timeline_item","description":[{"_key":"be12e753ff63","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"6b76802a3f66","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"以前只有上流社會才吃得起的肉，今天我們人人都可以享受得到。在人人都終於可以當食肉獸的今天，我們卻懷疑起肉來了：肉食是不是氣候變化的元凶？食肉是不是慢性自殺？肉攤上源源不絕的供應，會有停下來的一刻嗎？如果不能吃真的肉，那人造肉能代替肉嗎？透過尋尋常常的一塊肉，我們其實都有份在選擇一個不同的未來。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"f13edc8c0680","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"88c488bea3b80","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"無肉的未來：二十年後，你的乾炒牛河裡還有牛嗎？（預告）"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"fe151c3c61e1","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"767bbd98b6f50","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"桌上豬肉背後脆弱的供應鏈（預告）"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"2dcd8c16aad6","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"7aa5271c84240","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"實驗室裏的「人造肉」，會是替代選項嗎？（預告）"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"item_image":[{"_key":"be33a79b1867","_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-fc393eede1b181e2bb200dcb03883c22d60b4379-2160x1440-jpg","_type":"reference"},"published_time":"2022-08-01T13:09:02.925Z"}],"title":"「肉食動物」"},{"_key":"5ce3b0e8ee9f","_type":"timeline_item","description":[{"_key":"4ef6c5178dd1","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"80524f1b23d8","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"科技會更進步——對此我們似乎已經懶得去懷疑；即便如此，技術的進步與人類社會的進步之間，並非等號。也許，用「進步」來標籤未來的可能性，本身就散發著某種不安。與其想像未來，更難得的是擦亮眼睛看到當下。而今天的很多技術，已經在寫就我們想像中（或想像以外）的未來：我們一方面正擁有更多控制自己身體和生活的自由，一方面也似乎在失去了行動甚至思考的自由。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"7d1df0f0fcd6","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"5a1d617246210","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"世上最大規模的監控錄像建設項目，如何在中國展開？（預告）"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"66f9734f9640","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"603dc472ebd60","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"制裁下日益孤立的俄羅斯，監控技術哪裡來？（預告）"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"55775fc88652","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"ade2baff358e","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"（更多精彩待續）"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"7f481badccda","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"5409f3687aa50","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"\n"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"item_image":[{"_key":"4dc79cc0ec23","_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-5822f9252a7fb9f99b245da6a931c42daf9895eb-2160x1440-jpg","_type":"reference"},"published_time":"2022-08-01T13:08:29.958Z"}],"title":"「技術之眼」"}],"name":"我的未來，誰的選擇？端傳媒七週年專題｜端傳媒 Initium Media","slug":{"_type":"slug","current":"20220803-7th-year-special-reporting"},"theme_color":"#93ffc4"},"slug":"20220803-7th-year-special-reporting"},"__N_SSG":true}